<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.3.3">
<l>tuṅkamā maṇimāṭa neṭumukaṭṭiṉ cūlikaipōm</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷmā mukiltuṇikkun tirukkaṇṇa purattuṟaiyum</l>
<l>paiṅkaṇmāl viṭaiyaṭarttup paṉimatikōḷ viṭuttukanta</l>
<l>ceṅkaṇmā lammāṉuk kiḻantēṉeṉ ceṟivaḷaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I lost my clustered bangles to the bright-eyed dark lord who was glad</l>
<l>Having controlled the green-eyed dark bulls</l>
<l rend="indent">and dispelled the serpent of the cool moon,</l>
<l>[And] who dwells in Tirukkaṇṇapuram where the moon</l>
<l rend="indent">and dark clouds are rent</l>
<l>When they go [over] the finials on the high ridge tops</l>
<l rend="indent">of the great, renowned jeweled mansions.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
